{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/Whishlist_Now_Ingles.png?t=1730331534\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cards of Prophecy</strong> combines Tower Defense, Deckbuilding, and Roguelike elements, with huge inspiration from Trading Card Games.  <br>Build an ever evolving deck of spells and monsters. Fuse, defend, open card packs, create new strategies. Repeat.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Use your cards to summon incredible monsters and use powerful spells!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/SkeletonSummonAttack-Gif.gif?t=1730331534\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build your deck as you go, and discover strategies along the way. Every monster is special in their own way\u2013learn to master them and use them wisely!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your spells carefully! They may not be monsters, but that doesn't mean they aren't powerful.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each map is randomly generated and every round brings new challenges. Make sure to play strategically!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Fuse your cards into brand new monsters!</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/FusionsAttacking-Gif.gif?t=1730331534\" /></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With the &quot;Fusion&quot; spell card, you'll be able to fuse two monsters into a brand new monster with incredibly powerful effects!\u00a0</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Open a brand new pack of cards after each run! A whole collection of cards awaits!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/OpeningPack-Gif.gif?t=1730331534\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After each run, you'll earn gold to buy some brand new pack of cards, who knows what's inside? There might be some surprises...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are more than 100 cards to discover, each one will help you achieve victory in a different way!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Make a friend along the way</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/extras/DogAnimation-Gif.gif?t=1730331534\" /></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your little dog, Charly, will be with you on your adventures. Isn't he super cute?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every game mode has a different skin of your cute friend, which also has an unique Music according to him!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730331534","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1730331534","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/de2235129b8b7b1afd1d74113a686ba5ce8a385b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730331534","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/de2235129b8b7b1afd1d74113a686ba5ce8a385b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730331534","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":51},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256450/ext